### Which @angular/* package(s) are the source of the bug?

platform-browser

### Is this a regression?

Yes

### Description

so i have this CSP configuration
`add_header Content-Security-Policy "default-src 'self'; style-src 'self'; font-src *; img-src * data:; script-src 'self'; connect-src https://my.api-url.com";`

but this function in platform-browser.mjs line 372 trigger CSP error:
`_addStylesToHost(styles, host, styleNodes) {
        styles.forEach((style) => {
            const styleEl = this._doc.createElement('style');
            styleEl.textContent = style;
            styleNodes.push(host.appendChild(styleEl));
        });
    }`

is there any workaround for this issue without having to set unsafe-inline in CSP ?

